</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
21 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
