<P>
Kenyon to Rule on Lucky Merger: U.S. District Judge David Kenyon in Los Angeles 
has scheduled a hearing Tuesday at which he will consider what size bond 
California Atty. Gen. John K. Van de Kamp should be required to post to pursue 
his case against American Stores' merger of Lucky and Alpha Beta. The matter 
