<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
AIRLINES -- AUSTRALIA; PILOTS -- WAGES AND SALARIES; RESIGNATIONS; AIRLINES -- 
LABOR RELATIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
