designed and made for Nubian Princess in Ivory Coast. Delphine Wills-Martin in 
one of the beaded satin kufis she makes. Musician Dario Benjamin's reggae look 
includes hat from Nigeria, thrift-store vest, handmade leather shoes. Cookie 
Morris in elaborately braided hairdo and custom-made gold-black party outfit. 
SCOTT ROBINSON / Los Angeles Times; MINDY SCHAUER / Los Angeles Times; SCOTT 
